data.description:
Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in Clanton, Al. Situated on a spacious 16-acre lot this property offers a perfect blend of country living and modern convenience, with a new AC unit, new appliances, and a 3 year old roof.
The main level of the home features a spacious living room, a beautiful kitchen with updated appliances, sunroom, and a dining area. The master bedroom is also located on this level, along with two additional bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The downstairs basement area, is a versatile space that can be used as a mother-in-law suite, office area, or a man cave complete with a bedroom and full bathroom.
Outside, the property includes a horse stall area with a fenced-in pasture, perfect for equestrian enthusiasts. The kids will love playing in the creek that runs through the property! Back end of the property offers plenty of wooded areas, ideal for nature watching, hunting, and exploring. Additionally, the location of this home is convenient for shopping and schools, making it an ideal choice for families. Looking to have a small farm? This property is perfect! Whether you commute to Birmingham or Montgomery, this property offers easy access to major highways for a convenient commute. Don't miss the opportunity to own this beautiful home with plenty of space to spread out and enjoy the peaceful surroundings of Clanton, AL.
